short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Sets the background in Google Search page using arts from ArtStation.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension selects every 5 minute a random art from the ArtStation platform and uses it as a background on the Google Search pages.

For better experience the extension prefers the dark theme. If the light is selected it will automatically change it to the dark one.
